## Title
Mint

## URL
http://linuxmint.com

## Description
Very similar to Windows, easiest distribution to use. Works well out of the box. Comes with the Cinnamon desktop environment that looks nice and is intuitive.

## Pros
 - Very easy to install
 - Works out of the box
 - Codecs already installed
 - A lot of support
 
## Cons
 - Lots of newbish users
 - Holds your hand
 - The traditional UI can be boring (ala Windows)

